!елыннан, елымнан, елыңнан

!"dative G deletes after nasal-final possessive morphemes"
!%{G%}:0 <=> [ %{I%}: :NasalCns ]/[ %>: | :0 ] _ ;

"delete accusative н after px3"
н:0 <=> %{n%}: %>: _ %{I%}: .#. ;

"delete accusative {I} after px3"
